extends ModuleContentLinker
implements JaxRpcCodegenAdapter, ApplicationVisitor, EjbBundleVisitor, WebBundleVisitor, AppClientVisitor
    This class is responsible for generating all non portable jax-rpc artifacts for a single .ear or standalone module.
